#. type: Title ===
#: documentation/content/en/books/porters-handbook/security/chapter.adoc:173
#, no-wrap
msgid "Testing Changes to the VuXML Database"
msgstr "Prueba de cambios en la base de datos VuXML"

#. type: Plain text
#: documentation/content/en/books/porters-handbook/security/chapter.adoc:176
msgid ""
"This example describes a new entry for a vulnerability in the package "
"`dropbear` that has been fixed in version `dropbear-2013.59`."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: documentation/content/en/books/porters-handbook/security/chapter.adoc:178
msgid ""
"As a prerequisite, install a fresh version of package:security/vuxml[] port."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: documentation/content/en/books/porters-handbook/security/chapter.adoc:180
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"First, check whether there already is an entry for this vulnerability. If "
"there were such an entry, it would match the previous version of the "
"package, `2013.58`:"
msgstr ""
"Primero, verifique si ya existe una entrada para esta vulnerabilidad. Si "
"hubiera tal entrada, coincidiría con la versión anterior del paquete, "
"<literal>2013.58</literal>:"

#. type: delimited block . 4
#: documentation/content/en/books/porters-handbook/security/chapter.adoc:184
#, no-wrap
msgid "% pkg audit dropbear-2013.58\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: documentation/content/en/books/porters-handbook/security/chapter.adoc:187
msgid "If there is none found, add a new entry for this vulnerability."
msgstr ""
"Si no se encuentra ninguno, agregue una nueva entrada para esta "
"vulnerabilidad."

#. type: delimited block . 4
#: documentation/content/en/books/porters-handbook/security/chapter.adoc:192
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"% cd ${PORTSDIR}/security/vuxml\n"
"% make newentry\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: documentation/content/en/books/porters-handbook/security/chapter.adoc:195
msgid "Verify its syntax and formatting:"
msgstr "Verifique su sintaxis y formato:"

#. type: delimited block . 4
#: documentation/content/en/books/porters-handbook/security/chapter.adoc:199
#, no-wrap
msgid "% make validate\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: documentation/content/en/books/porters-handbook/security/chapter.adoc:203
msgid ""
"The previous command generates the [.filename]#vuln-flat.xml# file. It can "
"also be generated with:"
msgstr ""

#. type: delimited block . 4
#: documentation/content/en/books/porters-handbook/security/chapter.adoc:207
#, no-wrap
msgid "% make vuln-flat.xml\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: delimited block = 4
#: documentation/content/en/books/porters-handbook/security/chapter.adoc:212
msgid ""
"At least one of these packages needs to be installed: package:textproc/"
"libxml2[], package:textproc/jade[]."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: documentation/content/en/books/porters-handbook/security/chapter.adoc:215
msgid ""
"Verify that the `<affected>` section of the entry will match the correct "
"packages:"
msgstr ""

#. type: delimited block . 4
#: documentation/content/en/books/porters-handbook/security/chapter.adoc:219
#, no-wrap
msgid "% pkg audit -f ${PORTSDIR}/security/vuxml/vuln-flat.xml dropbear-2013.58\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: documentation/content/en/books/porters-handbook/security/chapter.adoc:222
msgid "Make sure that the entry produces no spurious matches in the output."
msgstr ""
"Asegúrese de que la entrada no produzca coincidencias falsas en la salida."

#. type: Plain text
#: documentation/content/en/books/porters-handbook/security/chapter.adoc:224
msgid "Now check whether the right package versions are matched by the entry:"
msgstr ""
"Ahora verifique si las versiones correctas del paquete coinciden con la "
"entrada:"

#. type: delimited block . 4
#: documentation/content/en/books/porters-handbook/security/chapter.adoc:233
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"% pkg audit -f ${PORTSDIR}/security/vuxml/vuln-flat.xml dropbear-2013.58 dropbear-2013.59\n"
"dropbear-2012.58 is vulnerable:\n"
"dropbear -- exposure of sensitive information, DoS\n"
"CVE: CVE-2013-4434\n"
"CVE: CVE-2013-4421\n"
"WWW: http://portaudit.FreeBSD.org/8c9b48d1-3715-11e3-a624-00262d8b701d.html\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: delimited block . 4
#: documentation/content/en/books/porters-handbook/security/chapter.adoc:235
#, no-wrap
msgid "1 problem(s) in the installed packages found.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: documentation/content/en/books/porters-handbook/security/chapter.adoc:237
msgid "The former version matches while the latter one does not."
msgstr "La primera versión coincide, mientras que la última no."
